title: Getting error while trying to train using a snapshot from a different project as init_weights
body:
### Is there an existing issue for this?

- [X] I have searched the existing issues

### Bug description

I have a big Master network that I have trained with different arenas and light conditions using about 40 videos. I have now decided to add the points of each arena to help with analysis, so I thought the best way of doing it is making a new project, add in the new labels to the already labeled data and train using as init_weight the last snapshot from the previously trained Master project. I couldnâ€™t manage to do it, it throws an error, does anyone have an advice?

### Operating System

Windows 10

### DeepLabCut version

dlc version 2.2.1.1

### DeepLabCut mode

single animal

### Device type

NVIDIA GPU 2080

### Steps To Reproduce

_No response_
